items.content_html: This is a Discord bot that utilizes OpenAI's GPT-3 API to generate creative prompts for MidJourney's AI image generation. It allows users to easily get prompt ideas in Discord by providing a natural language description. The bot is built with Discord.js and formats the AI-generated prompts to work seamlessly with MidJourney.
